        <abstract> 
<p>Asks that a copy of <hi rend="italic">Origin</hi> [3d ed.] be sent to Mlle Clémence-Auguste Royer; she has arranged with a publisher for a French translation.</p>  
<p><hi rend="italic">Origin</hi> is exciting much attention in Germany.</p> 
            <p>Surprised to receive a Dutch translation.</p>
            <p>Has never seen an advertisement [of 3d ed.], which is a pity. Hopes "Bishop of Oxford &amp; Co." have not made JM sorry he published it.</p>
        </abstract>
